.TH NET-FLAG 8 "June 2026" "cap-alert 1.0.4" "System Administration"
.SH NAME
net-flag \- suppress CAP-Alert alerts during nets
.SH SYNOPSIS
.B net-flag
.B on|off|status
.SH DESCRIPTION
Creates or clears /var/lib/cap-alert/linked.flag. While the flag is present,
.B cap-alert
skips alert playback so nets are not interrupted.
.PP
Like \fBcap-alert\fR, accepts \fBsudo net-flag\fR and runs as the \fBasterisk\fR user.
.SH SEE ALSO
.BR cap-alert (8)
